    In addition, we also have tried to fit $S(980)$ with K matrix formalism (Appendix~\ref{app:a0_f0_K_matrix}) checked the significance of non-resonance $K^{+}K^{-}$ S wave in $S(980)$ (Appendix~\ref{app:a0_f0_nonRes}).


